ADDING LOGOS AND TITLE 11

Step: Adding Colaberry Logo

Ø  Click on Insert from ribbon.

Ø  Then click on Image in Elements

Ø  Select the Image from the Extracted file

Ø  General:  X - Position = 0, Y - Position = 0, Width = 126 and Height = 97




Step: Adding Project Logo

Ø  Click on Insert from ribbon.

Ø  Then click on Image in Elements

Ø  Select the Image from the Extracted file

Ø  General:  X - Position = 116, Y - Position = 1, Width = 102 and Height = 96




Step: Adding Project Title 

Ø  Click on the Text box from Home or insert ribbon.

Ø  Begin typing the name of the project (Instructor Class Performance)

Ø  Turn the background to on position: Color : #596DBD, Transparency: 0%

Ø  Select the text then change the font size to 32 and font type to Constantia

Ø  select the text then font color to #000000 and Alignment center.

Ø  General:  X - Position = 0, Y - Position = 1, Width = 1258 and Height = 97

Ø  Border: set to on. Color: #B3B3B3, Radius: 0 px
